=======
Install
=======

To install this libary, just do the usual Python setup:

# tar -xvzf libgal3-*.tar.gz
# cd libgal3-*
# python setup.py install

That's it for install.  You should be able to import the libg3 library after
that:

(In your python script)
import libg3

